# Prototype Testing Recording

A screen recording was conducted to demonstrate the testing of the Peer Tutoring Platform prototype.  
The testing process was divided into **Student-side testing** and **Tutor-side testing** to verify the different system functions for each user role.

## Student Testing

The following features were tested from the student perspective:

- Register account
- Login to the platform
- Search tutor by subject
- View tutor profile
- Book tutoring session
- View booking status in "My Bookings"
- Rate tutor after session

